nginx (1.10.1-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * debian/control:
    + Drop nginx-*-dbg packages in favor of autogenerated -dbgsym packages.
    + Remove relic Breaks/Replaces from nginx-common.
    + Fix lsb-base dependencies.
