  [ Christos Trochalakis ]
  * Drop nginx-naxsi, nginx-naxsi-dbg, nginx-naxsi-ui packages.
    (Closes: #746199, #737146, #712445)
  * debian/conf/nginx.conf:
    + Remove relic passenger stanga.

