    + Changed ssl_protocols and ssl_ciphers. (Closes: 730142)
  * debian/nginx-common.preinst:
    + Modify permissions of /var/log/nginx. (Closes: #701112)
  * debian/rules:
    + Added spdy support to nginx-full. (Closes: #730432)

